show.title: Price of Love
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/pkaWDD
show.description: "Price of Love" is a raw, emotional rollercoaster tracing Jhanvi and Dhruva’s star-crossed love. From their spark in photography school to a painful breakup driven by secrets and sacrifice, life pulls them apart through betrayal, ambition, and class war. Years later, fate brings them face to face older, scarred, and holding truths they never dared to share. A hidden pregnancy, a sick child, financial ruin, and burning passion intertwine as love fights to rise from the ashes. But will pride and pain win, or can destiny heal what time shattered? It’s love, but not the kind you see in fairytales."
